QuestData.Title: What's Theirs is Ours
QuestData.Description: I found somethin' else while I was scoutin', boss.$B$BDa Alliance have a garrison just across da way, and der been no movement in or out of da place in a good while.$B$BDis be a golden opportunity to sack da place and bolster your coffers, commander.$B$BWhat do ya say? We do it together.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Shadow Hunter Ukambe at Admiral Taylor's Garrison.
QuestData.RewardText: Everyone be dead, mon. What did dis?
